{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Mandatory education and guidance on ethnic hair",
        "additional_details": "Introduce extensive and informative modules on afro Caribbean hair in schools.\r\n \r\nIn the workplace training is needed on discrimination against black people as well as information regarding the nature of hair in all its varieties. Overall resulting in the understanding that there are different types of hair that act in different ways.\r\n \r\nWe cannot make excuses for our ignorance any longer.",
        "background": "Compulsory education on the differences between human hair in the National curriculum and guidance for employers is needed.\r\n\r\nDiscrimination is most likely due to lack of knowledge and ignorance towards the variety in human beings.\r\n\r\nAcknowledgement of the nature of afro Caribbean hair would help!",
